\par }{\f100\fs22\lang1031\langfe1055\langnp1031\insrsid15939635 1986 y\'fdl\'fdnda Harvard'l\'fd kimyac\'fd Walter Gilbert ilk defa "RNA d\'fcnyas\'fd" terimini ortaya att\'fd. Gilbert bu terimi \'fe\'f6yle a\'e7\'fdkl\'fdyordu: "RNA molek\'fclleri ve birtak
