\par Evrimcileri RNA molek\'fcl\'fcn\'fcn hayat\'fdn ba\'felang\'fdc\'fd olabilece\'f0ini d\'fc\'fe\'fcnmeye iten nokta, canl\'fdlardaki RNA molek\'fcl\'fcn\'fcn kendi kendini kopyalama yetene\'f0ine sahip olmas\'fdyd\'fd. RNA molek\'fcl\'fc, h\'fccre i\'e7
