\'f0unu d\'fc\'fe\'fcn\'fcn. Diyelim ki bu monit\'f6rde her g\'fcn \'e7e\'feitli ki\'feilerin g\'f6r\'fcnt\'fcleri ve konu\'femalar belirsin. D\'fcnyan\'fdn farkl\'fd \'fclkelerinden farkl\'fd ki\'feiler, bu monit\'f6r arac\'fdl\'fd\'f0\'fd
